  "detailed_description": "Eraser is a survival game in a world of endless hardcore, where you improve with each unique battle.<br>Your goal is simple - survive, but it won't be that easy. Hoards of hungry and bloodthirsty mutants are waiting for the moment to tear you apart. Would you last for long enough?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level up</h2>Destroy the enemies by leveling up to improve your character and get stronger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/54f838fbdfbcf1cc288b11b166a63119.poster.avif?t=1683808740\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/54f838fbdfbcf1cc288b11b166a63119.webm?t=1683808740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/54f838fbdfbcf1cc288b11b166a63119.mp4?t=1683808740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Earn money, gain skills and unlock heroes</h2>Carnage lots of enemies to get more money which can be used to buy new weapons, improve your skills and unlock unique characters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/49fbf06a2ed8094fa94d6edaa3788df0.poster.avif?t=1683808740\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/49fbf06a2ed8094fa94d6edaa3788df0.webm?t=1683808740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/49fbf06a2ed8094fa94d6edaa3788df0.mp4?t=1683808740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variety</h2>Play on different maps encountering unique enemies and bosses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/d56bd79b03c9595ede569901f9d56346.poster.avif?t=1683808740\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/d56bd79b03c9595ede569901f9d56346.webm?t=1683808740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/d56bd79b03c9595ede569901f9d56346.mp4?t=1683808740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/06aafd016864cdc9db9b857081f1f52f.poster.avif?t=1683808740\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/06aafd016864cdc9db9b857081f1f52f.webm?t=1683808740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/06aafd016864cdc9db9b857081f1f52f.mp4?t=1683808740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sortie </h2>Each run can be completed in 30 minutes<br>In each sortie you pump up skills that enhance your character in the current sortie. You can combine different skills to get unique bundles for different situations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/52095f2917f09e35b6c3569c436809e2.poster.avif?t=1683808740\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/52095f2917f09e35b6c3569c436809e2.webm?t=1683808740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136470/extras/52095f2917f09e35b6c3569c436809e2.mp4?t=1683808740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >At the moment, Eraser contains:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 Maps with their own characteristics<br></li><li>4 Characters with unique characteristics<br></li><li>Lots of weapons<br></li><li>Different skills to improve the hero<br></li><li>Variety of enemies<br></li><li>Dynamic gameplay</li></ul>",
